name: OBAMAS LAST NAME
description: Sometime in early 2019 I made a map with the same song as this with a Thinking Space wave ahh part (but using the UFO instead). While building it, I lost my data and was quite angry since I actually spent effort making it, so I made a new map with the same song but made it as shitty as possible. This map too would also become lost but @syberchase still had a copy for some reason.
